1
00:00:39,710 --> 00:00:40,550
Gentlemen,

2
00:00:41,110 --> 00:00:42,710
I know you can't wait.

3
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:46,280
Our amazing team

4
00:00:47,030 --> 00:00:49,640
is getting tonight's surprise ready for you.

5
00:00:50,320 --> 00:00:51,280
Everything here

6
00:00:51,840 --> 00:00:54,560
will be something you've never

7
00:00:56,150 --> 00:00:57,280
experienced before.

8
00:00:57,840 --> 00:00:58,680
Great.

9
00:01:58,580 --> 00:02:02,460
=The Hidden Truth=

10
00:02:02,460 --> 00:02:05,100
=Episode 7=

11
00:02:05,100 --> 00:02:08,940
(Qingcheng Public Security Bureau)

12
00:02:08,940 --> 00:02:13,220
(Personnel Files)

13
00:02:18,930 --> 00:02:19,780
Meeting time.

14
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,870
What's with you? Come on.

15
00:02:29,150 --> 00:02:31,000
Liu, give us the rundown.

16
00:02:31,750 --> 00:02:32,780
The information is solid.

17
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:34,960
The two dog thieves confessed everything.

18
00:02:35,190 --> 00:02:36,030
There's a direct link

19
00:02:36,150 --> 00:02:38,400
between Hongyun, the shelter, and the casino.

20
00:02:39,060 --> 00:02:39,990
Let's grab Zhang Ming.

21
00:02:40,630 --> 00:02:42,030
Bring him in and interrogate him.

22
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:44,400
That'll connect all the dots

23
00:02:44,730 --> 00:02:46,140
and lead us to the key evidence.

24
00:02:46,220 --> 00:02:47,150
We can't arrest him yet.

25
00:02:47,430 --> 00:02:49,710
We don't know how deeply
Zhang Ming is involved.

26
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:52,280
If he doesn't know much,

27
00:02:52,720 --> 00:02:54,090
bringing him in won't help.

28
00:02:54,310 --> 00:02:56,030
It'll only make them lie low,

29
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:58,680
and then it'll be harder to find evidence.

30
00:02:59,190 --> 00:03:00,680
If he is a key figure,

31
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:03,240
arresting him now will tip them off,

32
00:03:03,710 --> 00:03:05,960
and the real people behind it

33
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,360
will disappear.

34
00:03:07,870 --> 00:03:08,800
You're overthinking it.

35
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:12,240
Zhang Ming directly contacted the thieves.

36
00:03:12,430 --> 00:03:14,960
The dog poisoning caused chaos citywide.

37
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,360
They're the main culprits.

38
00:03:17,030 --> 00:03:18,680
We meant to play the long game.

39
00:03:19,870 --> 00:03:20,910
But after we arrested them,

40
00:03:20,910 --> 00:03:22,120
things turned out differently.

41
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,360
Clearer, actually.

42
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,800
Don't think I don't know

43
00:03:26,030 --> 00:03:27,090
what you're worried about.

44
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,710
Whether you like it or not,

45
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:32,750
Wang Li is a suspect in this case.

46
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:35,280
As for whether it hurts Wang Yimo,

47
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:37,590
that's not our concern right now.

48
00:03:40,070 --> 00:03:41,560
I'm not thinking about anything else.

49
00:03:42,750 --> 00:03:45,240
I want Zhang Ming arrested,

50
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,150
held down,

51
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:48,030
and questioned.

52
00:03:48,190 --> 00:03:49,470
Same as the two thieves.

53
00:03:49,470 --> 00:03:50,350
Make him name the guy,

54
00:03:50,370 --> 00:03:51,840
and we close the case.

55
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:52,960
It's not the same.

56
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:55,680
Those petty crooks barely knew anything.

57
00:03:56,310 --> 00:03:58,120
Them giving key info was luck.

58
00:03:58,330 --> 00:03:59,600
You've been after it.

59
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:00,800
Did you find it?

60
00:04:01,030 --> 00:04:02,120
That was coincidence.

61
00:04:02,630 --> 00:04:05,030
You can't base actions on coincidence.

62
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,360
Here's what we do.

63
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:09,870
Coordinate with local and traffic police.

64
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:11,420
Expand surveillance coverage.

65
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:12,840
Put these key people

66
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:14,590
under watch.

67
00:04:14,750 --> 00:04:16,040
Once we have enough evidence,

68
00:04:16,370 --> 00:04:17,680
we take them all down at once.

69
00:04:17,940 --> 00:04:18,880
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

70
00:04:22,510 --> 00:04:23,350
Yes, sir.

71
00:04:28,260 --> 00:04:32,180
(Hongyun Restaurant)

72
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:37,310
Extra dishes on the house.

73
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:38,840
Enjoy.

74
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,120
What's this about?

75
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,560
Around here,

76
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:44,040
most customers are regulars.

77
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:46,070
You two must be new.

78
00:04:46,750 --> 00:04:47,830
Thanks for coming.

79
00:04:48,310 --> 00:04:49,560
Food okay?

80
00:04:49,750 --> 00:04:50,590
Yeah, it's good.

81
00:04:50,870 --> 00:04:51,710
Pretty good.

82
00:04:51,810 --> 00:04:53,380
Wouldn't come every day if it wasn't.

83
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,400
Good.

84
00:04:54,750 --> 00:04:56,190
If you like it, come often.

85
00:04:56,190 --> 00:04:57,160
Thanks for the support.

86
00:04:57,750 --> 00:04:59,230
- Enjoy.
- Thanks.

87
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,080
Eat up.

88
00:05:18,630 --> 00:05:20,360
I've never seen those guys downstairs.

89
00:05:22,070 --> 00:05:22,910
These past few days,

90
00:05:24,750 --> 00:05:26,390
they show up for lunch and dinner.

91
00:05:29,310 --> 00:05:30,360
We should stay alert.

92
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:34,560
Ali,

93
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:37,160
you think something's off?

94
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,680
Could be cops.

95
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,630
Could be Bai's people.

96
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:48,310
Last time you two trashed his kitchen,

97
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:51,480
is there something you didn't tell me?

98
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:53,200
No.

99
00:05:54,830 --> 00:05:55,680
I didn't do anything.

100
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:58,510
Probably not.

101
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,000
Probably?

102
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:04,040
What do you mean, probably?

103
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:07,520
No.

104
00:06:07,750 --> 00:06:09,480
I just thought it over carefully.

105
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:10,840
There's nothing.

106
00:06:17,190 --> 00:06:18,560
Things are sensitive right now.

107
00:06:19,390 --> 00:06:20,750
Don't hide anything from me.

108
00:06:20,750 --> 00:06:22,000
If something happened, tell me.

109
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,430
Stay sharp.

110
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,750
Are you doing okay now?

111
00:07:17,270 --> 00:07:18,110
Yeah.

112
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:20,720
Is Dad treating you well?

113
00:07:22,430 --> 00:07:23,270
Yes.

114
00:07:59,510 --> 00:08:01,000
You can't keep missing payments.

115
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:02,080
One more time

116
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,720
and if the system cuts you off,

117
00:08:03,830 --> 00:08:05,480
you won't be able to buy cold meds.

118
00:08:09,900 --> 00:08:14,220
(Ward 4)

119
00:08:41,100 --> 00:08:43,580
(Wang Yimo)

120
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:47,870
Sorry,

121
00:08:47,870 --> 00:08:50,670
the number you dialed
is currently unavailable.

122
00:08:50,870 --> 00:08:52,150
Please try again later.

123
00:08:52,580 --> 00:08:53,900
(Wang Yimo)

124
00:08:56,860 --> 00:08:59,020
(Zhang Jiali)

125
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:07,150
Hello, the number you dialed...

126
00:09:07,740 --> 00:09:10,020
(Contacts)

127
00:09:10,020 --> 00:09:11,860
(Bai)

128
00:09:13,630 --> 00:09:14,910
If anything comes up,

129
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,280
call me.

130
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:18,790
If I can help, I will.

131
00:09:23,060 --> 00:09:25,900
(Bai)

132
00:09:51,630 --> 00:09:53,870
Ali, Zhang Ming went into the casino.

133
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,440
Should I keep following?

134
00:09:55,630 --> 00:09:56,470
No.

135
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:57,800
Go home.

136
00:09:57,880 --> 00:09:59,110
Don't come back either.

137
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:00,800
Okay.

138
00:10:13,750 --> 00:10:14,590
Mr. Bai,

139
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:17,960
I'm in trouble.

140
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:20,320
The police might come for me anytime.

141
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:23,200
I don't know what your plan is,

142
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:25,000
but I'm still useful.

143
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:25,840
I can help you.

144
00:10:26,150 --> 00:10:27,150
But I need money.

145
00:10:28,150 --> 00:10:29,120
I need a lot of money

146
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,200
to take my mom away.

147
00:10:35,510 --> 00:10:36,350
Sit.

148
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:45,960
Ming.

149
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:47,680
No need to rush.

150
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:50,320
The police haven't found you yet.

151
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:51,800
I can handle

152
00:10:52,630 --> 00:10:53,750
your problem.

153
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:56,840
Thank you, Mr. Bai.

154
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:09,200
This is...

155
00:11:11,750 --> 00:11:13,030
Found a companion for the mute.

156
00:11:15,510 --> 00:11:16,350
Nice.

157
00:11:17,020 --> 00:11:18,040
What's his disability?

158
00:11:18,670 --> 00:11:19,720
His name's Zhang Ming.

159
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:21,630
He's Wang Li's accountant.

160
00:11:22,790 --> 00:11:25,360
Back when the clubhouse kitchen
got smashed up,

161
00:11:25,910 --> 00:11:26,840
he was there too.

162
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,550
Didn't I tell you?

163
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:32,670
I'll cover your losses.

164
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,750
That's why I brought him today.

165
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:37,840
Mr. Bai,

166
00:11:39,630 --> 00:11:40,470
what does this mean?

167
00:11:41,670 --> 00:11:42,600
You want me to pay?

168
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:45,120
Qiang smashed the kitchen.

169
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:47,030
I tried to stop him, but I couldn't.

170
00:11:47,270 --> 00:11:48,440
Didn't you say you'd help me?

171
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:50,080
Now you want me to pay?

172
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:51,550
I don't have money.

173
00:11:51,550 --> 00:11:52,840
Not a cent.

174
00:11:53,510 --> 00:11:54,670
Okay, sit, sit.

175
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:55,680
Sit down.

176
00:11:57,510 --> 00:11:59,000
Who said you're paying?

177
00:12:00,150 --> 00:12:00,950
I told you it's got

178
00:12:00,980 --> 00:12:02,200
nothing to do with you.

179
00:12:02,910 --> 00:12:03,910
Why are you so nervous?

180
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:08,030
Then what are you two doing here?

181
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:10,360
Talking over each other

182
00:12:10,360 --> 00:12:11,220
and putting on a show?

183
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:12,150
You think I'm stupid?

184
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:14,840
Just give me a straight answer.

185
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:16,120
Is he paying?

186
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:17,720
Or should I sell him to settle the debt?

187
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:18,800
Say it.

188
00:12:19,150 --> 00:12:19,990
Neither.

189
00:12:20,910 --> 00:12:22,720
He won't pay a dime.

190
00:12:23,150 --> 00:12:24,440
But with him around,

191
00:12:25,150 --> 00:12:26,600
someone else will.

192
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,790
You're negotiating with Wang Li, right?

193
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:34,120
Take him with you to Hongyun later.

194
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:36,040
I'll come after.

195
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,040
Then,

196
00:12:37,670 --> 00:12:38,790
you'll understand.

197
00:12:43,910 --> 00:12:45,200
Always so mysterious.

198
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:52,440
Where are you going?

199
00:12:52,870 --> 00:12:54,320
Why not go together?

200
00:12:54,670 --> 00:12:56,360
Things are tense right now.

201
00:12:56,910 --> 00:12:58,630
Too many people draws attention.

202
00:13:00,550 --> 00:13:01,390
Relax.

203
00:13:01,870 --> 00:13:02,710
I'm not running.

204
00:13:06,670 --> 00:13:07,630
Pointless.

205
00:13:19,030 --> 00:13:19,870
Mr. Bai.

206
00:13:20,960 --> 00:13:21,800
Don't worry.

207
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:24,240
Once it's done,

208
00:13:25,140 --> 00:13:26,250
however much you want,

209
00:13:27,510 --> 00:13:28,670
I'll give it to you.

210
00:13:31,630 --> 00:13:32,470
Thanks, Mr. Bai.

211
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:04,030
Why aren't we going together?

212
00:14:04,030 --> 00:14:06,030
What are you waiting for?

213
00:14:06,870 --> 00:14:08,720
They're figuring out how to deal with me.

214
00:14:09,150 --> 00:14:10,240
We'll go in later.

215
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:12,960
Give them time to talk.

216
00:14:18,030 --> 00:14:19,960
They're plotting against you,

217
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:21,360
and you're sleeping here?

218
00:14:22,320 --> 00:14:23,550
You're telling me what to do?

219
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:27,790
They think cooperating

220
00:14:27,790 --> 00:14:29,030
means they can cut me out.

221
00:14:30,600 --> 00:14:32,150
Give them some space and time.

222
00:14:34,110 --> 00:14:35,070
Let's wait a bit longer.

223
00:14:36,240 --> 00:14:37,360
You'll see soon enough.

224
00:14:43,980 --> 00:14:46,660
(A mysterious figure?)

225
00:14:46,670 --> 00:14:48,320
Okay.

226
00:14:48,790 --> 00:14:49,630
Got it.

227
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:50,840
Captain Zhao.

228
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:52,200
Everyone's in position.

229
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:53,680
Good.

230
00:14:55,150 --> 00:14:55,990
Master.

231
00:14:57,270 --> 00:14:58,960
Are we wrong

232
00:14:59,150 --> 00:15:00,200
about Wang Li?

233
00:15:01,910 --> 00:15:02,790
If he's tied

234
00:15:03,750 --> 00:15:05,790
to Liu Yan's case,

235
00:15:06,270 --> 00:15:09,000
his movements and connections don't match.

236
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:11,910
If it's the Naked Banquet Case,

237
00:15:12,390 --> 00:15:13,650
we don't have solid evidence.

238
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:19,960
I've told you so many times,

239
00:15:19,960 --> 00:15:20,960
stop chewing on pen caps.

240
00:15:21,180 --> 00:15:22,320
Put anything in your mouth.

241
00:15:22,550 --> 00:15:23,390
How old are you?

242
00:15:25,150 --> 00:15:25,990
Liu.

243
00:15:33,790 --> 00:15:35,150
Wang Li's profile.

244
00:15:35,150 --> 00:15:38,580
(Class of 1990,
Huaxin Middle School, Qingcheng)

245
00:15:38,600 --> 00:15:39,440
Look here.

246
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:42,440
Wang Li in middle school.

247
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:44,280
This guy.

248
00:15:49,630 --> 00:15:50,480
Bai Qiming?

249
00:15:52,080 --> 00:15:52,920
Bai?

250
00:15:57,390 --> 00:15:59,750
He and Wang Li were classmates.

251
00:16:00,980 --> 00:16:04,260
(Class of 1990,
Huaxin Middle School, Qingcheng)

252
00:16:11,320 --> 00:16:12,160
Mr. Li,

253
00:16:12,750 --> 00:16:14,960
what's this about with Wang Li?

254
00:16:21,870 --> 00:16:24,510
Do you know what Bai wants?

255
00:16:36,030 --> 00:16:37,750
You two better give me an answer.

256
00:16:39,240 --> 00:16:40,390
My name's Bai Qiming.

257
00:16:41,630 --> 00:16:42,840
Just call me Bai.

258
00:16:43,550 --> 00:16:44,910
Give me five minutes.

259
00:16:45,320 --> 00:16:46,840
If you're not interested after that,

260
00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:48,750
you can throw me out anytime.

261
00:16:50,240 --> 00:16:52,510
(Bagong Dog Shelter)
Say something worth my time.

262
00:16:52,750 --> 00:16:53,930
Or, neither of you is leaving.

263
00:16:57,200 --> 00:16:58,040
Mr. Li,

264
00:16:59,080 --> 00:17:01,240
I came with sincerity.

265
00:17:03,120 --> 00:17:04,160
Give me an account number.

266
00:17:04,160 --> 00:17:05,680
I'll wire you 200,000 right now.

267
00:17:06,590 --> 00:17:08,110
Consider it

268
00:17:10,270 --> 00:17:11,110
a meeting gift.

269
00:17:15,400 --> 00:17:17,510
Looks like you're serious.

270
00:17:20,720 --> 00:17:21,680
Get to the point.

271
00:17:22,400 --> 00:17:23,240
What do you want?

272
00:17:25,830 --> 00:17:27,680
Live-stream dog sales.

273
00:17:28,110 --> 00:17:30,000
Cut loose the small stuff at the casino.

274
00:17:31,720 --> 00:17:33,510
Who's buying dogs on livestreams?

275
00:17:34,070 --> 00:17:35,880
The shelter doesn't make money.

276
00:17:36,070 --> 00:17:37,400
Not losing money would be a win.

277
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:38,480
I'd make more

278
00:17:38,480 --> 00:17:39,440
renting this place out.

279
00:17:42,750 --> 00:17:44,750
That's called an information gap.

280
00:17:45,750 --> 00:17:47,480
Livestreaming isn't just about selling dogs.

281
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:50,830
It's about selling emotion.

282
00:17:51,880 --> 00:17:53,750
Round up a few hundred stray dogs.

283
00:17:54,100 --> 00:17:55,400
The worse they look, the better.

284
00:17:56,440 --> 00:17:58,550
Trigger donations
from so-called animal lovers.

285
00:17:59,350 --> 00:18:01,270
Make netizens think you're doing charity

286
00:18:01,590 --> 00:18:02,440
and good deeds.

287
00:18:02,590 --> 00:18:03,510
The key point is

288
00:18:05,110 --> 00:18:06,270
once your income

289
00:18:06,550 --> 00:18:07,720
gets traced,

290
00:18:08,640 --> 00:18:11,270
it's illegal money.

291
00:18:16,790 --> 00:18:17,920
Here comes my resources.

292
00:18:18,350 --> 00:18:20,640
I take part of your earnings

293
00:18:20,640 --> 00:18:22,200
and invest it overseas.

294
00:18:23,160 --> 00:18:24,720
When that money comes back,

295
00:18:25,240 --> 00:18:27,070
it's completely clean.

296
00:18:28,070 --> 00:18:29,480
And the returns are huge.

297
00:18:31,350 --> 00:18:32,720
Those foreign ventures

298
00:18:33,030 --> 00:18:34,200
are easy money.

299
00:19:01,780 --> 00:19:04,860
(Hongyun Restaurant)

300
00:19:10,580 --> 00:19:12,860
(Welcome)

301
00:19:20,960 --> 00:19:21,800
Let's go.

302
00:19:27,020 --> 00:19:28,340
(Hongyun Restaurant)

303
00:19:32,640 --> 00:19:33,500
Captain Zhao,

304
00:19:33,590 --> 00:19:34,830
our stake-out just caught

305
00:19:34,830 --> 00:19:36,790
Zhang Ming and Li Xu went
into Hongyun together.

306
00:19:38,030 --> 00:19:39,400
How did those two end up together?

307
00:19:46,440 --> 00:19:48,960
Zhang Ming's ties to them just got closer.

308
00:19:51,220 --> 00:19:54,700
(Teahouse Shareholder;
Shelter Shareholder)

309
00:19:55,680 --> 00:19:56,520
Mr. Wang,

310
00:20:01,510 --> 00:20:02,510
you seem in a good mood.

311
00:20:02,960 --> 00:20:03,920
Enjoying the view?

312
00:20:11,350 --> 00:20:12,440
He came with me.

313
00:20:12,790 --> 00:20:14,670
But don't ask me.

314
00:20:14,790 --> 00:20:15,720
I don't know why either.

315
00:20:17,200 --> 00:20:18,040
Ming.

316
00:20:18,310 --> 00:20:19,150
Yes.

317
00:20:19,920 --> 00:20:20,770
Make some tea.

318
00:20:20,830 --> 00:20:21,670
Okay.

319
00:20:25,240 --> 00:20:26,080
Exactly.

320
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:27,510
My guy came along with you.

321
00:20:27,510 --> 00:20:28,940
It wouldn't be right for me to ask.

322
00:20:31,920 --> 00:20:33,070
Seriously.

323
00:20:33,070 --> 00:20:33,910
What's up with you?

324
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:35,270
Why dragging things out?

325
00:20:35,680 --> 00:20:36,920
Didn't I just say that earlier?

326
00:20:36,920 --> 00:20:38,590
I don't know, stop asking me.

327
00:20:39,310 --> 00:20:40,200
Got it?

328
00:20:41,480 --> 00:20:42,320
Relax.

329
00:20:42,770 --> 00:20:44,240
Someone will explain it to you later.

330
00:20:45,640 --> 00:20:46,480
Fine.

331
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:47,480
Let's talk business.

332
00:20:48,200 --> 00:20:49,160
The cooperation.

333
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:51,110
What do you think?

334
00:20:57,160 --> 00:20:58,350
Here's what I think.

335
00:20:59,000 --> 00:21:00,240
I think your restaurant

336
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:02,170
doesn't need major changes.

337
00:21:02,980 --> 00:21:03,830
Once I'm involved,

338
00:21:03,830 --> 00:21:05,310
we'll just renovate

339
00:21:05,310 --> 00:21:06,760
the private rooms on the third floor.

340
00:21:07,030 --> 00:21:07,880
VIP reception.

341
00:21:08,400 --> 00:21:09,510
My business

342
00:21:10,070 --> 00:21:10,910
stays the same.

343
00:21:12,270 --> 00:21:13,590
We maximize profits.

344
00:21:14,200 --> 00:21:15,960
Think long term. What do you say?

345
00:21:16,640 --> 00:21:17,920
Whatever you need, say it.

346
00:21:18,310 --> 00:21:19,830
I'll do it.

347
00:21:22,030 --> 00:21:22,870
Ali.

348
00:21:29,830 --> 00:21:31,480
Since we're partnering,

349
00:21:31,920 --> 00:21:32,880
shouldn't we

350
00:21:33,440 --> 00:21:35,640
sort things out too?

351
00:21:40,920 --> 00:21:42,030
I still have

352
00:21:43,200 --> 00:21:44,750
some accounts to sort out.

353
00:21:45,440 --> 00:21:46,550
Once I do,

354
00:21:47,350 --> 00:21:48,350
it'll be handled.

355
00:22:02,880 --> 00:22:03,880
Greetings, my friends.

356
00:22:04,590 --> 00:22:07,030
You two met for tea and didn't invite me.

357
00:22:08,310 --> 00:22:09,480
That's cold.

358
00:22:12,870 --> 00:22:14,090
What are you doing here?

359
00:22:15,240 --> 00:22:16,080
Why?

360
00:22:16,720 --> 00:22:18,030
You can talk to Mr. Li

361
00:22:20,880 --> 00:22:21,960
but I can't know about it?

362
00:22:23,790 --> 00:22:24,960
What we talked about

363
00:22:25,510 --> 00:22:26,750
is not about you.

364
00:22:26,920 --> 00:22:27,760
Today,

365
00:22:28,270 --> 00:22:29,440
I don't have time for you.

366
00:22:30,640 --> 00:22:31,480
Ming,

367
00:22:33,720 --> 00:22:34,560
see him out.

368
00:22:36,750 --> 00:22:37,590
Bai,

369
00:22:37,880 --> 00:22:40,070
you send me ahead
just so you can show off?

370
00:22:40,070 --> 00:22:40,910
Seriously?

371
00:22:41,590 --> 00:22:42,920
Does it make you feel special

372
00:22:42,920 --> 00:22:44,240
to have everyone waiting on you?

373
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:46,040
Mr. Li,

374
00:22:46,160 --> 00:22:47,960
stop undermining me.

375
00:22:49,070 --> 00:22:50,790
You two needed to talk.

376
00:22:51,200 --> 00:22:52,510
I shouldn't be involved.

377
00:22:52,880 --> 00:22:54,310
I was giving you space.

378
00:22:54,680 --> 00:22:56,200
Right, Mr. Wang?

379
00:22:57,960 --> 00:23:00,350
Fine. Since everyone's here,

380
00:23:00,880 --> 00:23:02,200
let's stop hiding things.

381
00:23:02,800 --> 00:23:04,240
Let's put it all on the table today.

382
00:23:05,830 --> 00:23:07,840
That's better, isn't it?

383
00:23:07,960 --> 00:23:09,400
Should've done this earlier.

384
00:23:09,790 --> 00:23:10,640
See?

385
00:23:11,430 --> 00:23:12,590
If everyone had this attitude,

386
00:23:12,680 --> 00:23:13,680
we'd be fine already.

387
00:23:13,960 --> 00:23:15,720
All right.

388
00:23:17,070 --> 00:23:17,920
I'll be blunt.

389
00:23:18,440 --> 00:23:20,440
I have a way to compensate your losses.

390
00:23:21,880 --> 00:23:23,110
Right here.

391
00:23:26,030 --> 00:23:26,920
Ask him for the money.

392
00:23:27,550 --> 00:23:29,310
That's your solution?

393
00:23:31,510 --> 00:23:32,680
You're insane.

394
00:23:33,510 --> 00:23:35,440
If I were going to ask him for money,

395
00:23:35,440 --> 00:23:36,700
I wouldn't need you to tell me.

396
00:23:37,160 --> 00:23:38,270
He owes you money.

397
00:23:38,790 --> 00:23:40,790
Not just for trashing the clubhouse.

398
00:23:41,310 --> 00:23:43,880
He owes you big money.

399
00:23:46,640 --> 00:23:48,720
Can you just say it clearly?

400
00:23:48,830 --> 00:23:49,670
I can.

401
00:23:51,550 --> 00:23:53,350
Once I do, you'll get it.

402
00:23:54,400 --> 00:23:55,240
The shelter money.

403
00:23:55,720 --> 00:23:56,790
Did you receive it all?

404
00:23:58,830 --> 00:24:01,000
I don't know what you two talked about,

405
00:24:01,680 --> 00:24:03,200
but for your safety,

406
00:24:03,550 --> 00:24:04,480
the livestream money

407
00:24:04,750 --> 00:24:06,550
was never put in your account.

408
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:07,790
You know that, right?

409
00:24:08,550 --> 00:24:09,390
So,

410
00:24:09,550 --> 00:24:10,750
Wang Li and I worked together

411
00:24:11,480 --> 00:24:12,440
and temporarily

412
00:24:12,750 --> 00:24:14,440
routed the money to him.

413
00:24:14,920 --> 00:24:15,920
To this day,

414
00:24:16,110 --> 00:24:18,000
he hasn't given me a single cent.

415
00:24:19,400 --> 00:24:20,240
What did you say?

416
00:24:20,240 --> 00:24:21,680
I don't understand a word.

417
00:24:21,880 --> 00:24:23,070
But I get one thing.

418
00:24:24,110 --> 00:24:25,590
You're both scammers.

419
00:24:26,480 --> 00:24:28,830
I hate being lied to more than anything.

420
00:24:29,030 --> 00:24:31,640
Now I know why you made me come early.

421
00:24:32,640 --> 00:24:33,480
Fine.

422
00:24:33,750 --> 00:24:34,590
Today,

423
00:24:35,680 --> 00:24:37,200
if this doesn't get cleared up,

424
00:24:37,260 --> 00:24:38,310
if there's no conclusion,

425
00:24:38,310 --> 00:24:39,720
nobody leaves this room.

426
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:42,550
Mr. Li, don't get angry.

427
00:24:42,960 --> 00:24:43,960
I would never lie to you.

428
00:24:44,750 --> 00:24:46,030
What he said

429
00:24:46,920 --> 00:24:48,160
has nothing to do with me.

430
00:24:48,310 --> 00:24:49,830
Nothing to do with you?

431
00:24:51,000 --> 00:24:51,840
Zhang Ming,

432
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:54,750
give me the card you withdraw money from.

433
00:25:05,480 --> 00:25:08,640
All the livestream money went
into Zhang Ming's card.

434
00:25:10,920 --> 00:25:11,880
He's your guy.

435
00:25:12,270 --> 00:25:14,240
And you're saying
it has nothing to do with you?

436
00:25:17,720 --> 00:25:18,560
Ali,

437
00:25:19,720 --> 00:25:20,560
this…

438
00:25:20,640 --> 00:25:21,480
this card…

439
00:25:21,640 --> 00:25:22,510
the money in it…

440
00:25:22,590 --> 00:25:24,680
I… I don't know what kind of money this is.

441
00:25:24,960 --> 00:25:25,920
I made a withdrawal.

442
00:25:26,920 --> 00:25:28,550
But honestly, I have no idea.

443
00:25:43,240 --> 00:25:44,080
I swear

444
00:25:44,600 --> 00:25:46,190
this is the first time I've seen it.

445
00:25:46,270 --> 00:25:48,350
You can check the bank records.

446
00:25:48,590 --> 00:25:49,480
That can't lie.

447
00:25:52,380 --> 00:25:53,780
(Self-Service Bank)

448
00:26:01,400 --> 00:26:02,540
Please take your cash.

449
00:26:03,270 --> 00:26:04,110
All right.

450
00:26:04,270 --> 00:26:05,110
(Self-Service Bank)
Then let's check.

451
00:26:06,070 --> 00:26:07,440
See who withdrew the money.

452
00:26:08,180 --> 00:26:09,590
(Cash)
Zhang Ming,

453
00:26:09,880 --> 00:26:11,790
I only kept the card because I trusted you.

454
00:26:11,790 --> 00:26:13,240
Please retrieve your card.

455
00:26:13,240 --> 00:26:15,030
How dare you touch this money?

456
00:26:15,640 --> 00:26:16,790
All this time,

457
00:26:17,030 --> 00:26:18,860
how much did you and your boss
skim off me?

458
00:26:18,860 --> 00:26:20,030
(Self-Service Banking)

459
00:26:20,030 --> 00:26:21,350
You used my trust.

460
00:26:21,350 --> 00:26:22,680
You lied to me. To everyone.

461
00:26:24,480 --> 00:26:25,320
You set me up.

462
00:26:27,590 --> 00:26:29,440
You framed me, Bai.

463
00:26:29,920 --> 00:26:32,010
You think you're worth
the effort of a setup?

464
00:26:32,400 --> 00:26:33,250
Don't forget.

465
00:26:33,270 --> 00:26:35,480
You called me first, asking for help.

466
00:26:36,070 --> 00:26:37,510
Why don't you ask your boss

467
00:26:37,830 --> 00:26:38,670
where that money

468
00:26:39,030 --> 00:26:41,070
actually went?

469
00:26:47,880 --> 00:26:48,720
Mr. Bai…

470
00:26:50,510 --> 00:26:51,880
Mr. Bai… Ali…

471
00:26:52,920 --> 00:26:56,030
Mr. Li, my... my mom is sick.

472
00:26:56,750 --> 00:26:58,030
I can't get into trouble.

473
00:26:58,960 --> 00:26:59,800
If I do,

474
00:26:59,830 --> 00:27:01,270
she's done.

475
00:27:01,720 --> 00:27:04,070
You're all big bosses.

476
00:27:04,270 --> 00:27:06,160
Please let me go.

477
00:27:06,960 --> 00:27:08,640
You're all big shots.

478
00:27:08,880 --> 00:27:10,110
Don't hold it against me.

479
00:27:10,110 --> 00:27:11,880
I'm begging you!

480
00:27:21,590 --> 00:27:23,240
I finally get it.

481
00:27:24,270 --> 00:27:26,400
Both of you are scammers.

482
00:27:27,790 --> 00:27:29,240
Every last one of you.

483
00:27:31,480 --> 00:27:32,320
Bai,

484
00:27:33,480 --> 00:27:34,680
our deal is easy to settle.

485
00:27:35,240 --> 00:27:36,080
Wang Li,

486
00:27:36,230 --> 00:27:37,750
our business is easy, too.

487
00:27:38,160 --> 00:27:40,030
But whatever's between you two,

488
00:27:40,550 --> 00:27:42,030
I don't care.

489
00:27:43,270 --> 00:27:44,590
I only want my money.

490
00:27:45,920 --> 00:27:46,760
Understand?

491
00:27:49,830 --> 00:27:51,110
As for your mess,

492
00:27:54,240 --> 00:27:55,920
I'll give you time to sort it out.

493
00:27:56,400 --> 00:27:58,400
If you can't,

494
00:28:00,310 --> 00:28:01,480
this time next year,

495
00:28:03,750 --> 00:28:05,110
you'll be six feet under.

496
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:26,000
Bai,

497
00:28:26,920 --> 00:28:27,790
you won

498
00:28:29,480 --> 00:28:30,320
this round.

499
00:28:31,920 --> 00:28:32,760
Name your terms.

500
00:28:33,790 --> 00:28:34,630
Terms?

501
00:28:35,590 --> 00:28:37,270
Think you're qualified to talk terms?

502
00:28:38,750 --> 00:28:39,790
Look at you now.

503
00:28:40,480 --> 00:28:42,510
Even your right-hand man of ten years

504
00:28:42,510 --> 00:28:43,590
dares to betray you.

505
00:28:44,110 --> 00:28:45,750
What do you have to bargain with?

506
00:28:58,000 --> 00:28:59,510
I'll ask you one last time.

507
00:29:02,880 --> 00:29:04,200
What do you want?

508
00:29:12,480 --> 00:29:13,550
Not telling you.

509
00:29:18,550 --> 00:29:20,110
I'll kill you!

510
00:29:29,830 --> 00:29:30,880
So we're playing dirty now?

511
00:29:32,070 --> 00:29:33,270
No more pretending now.

512
00:29:34,080 --> 00:29:35,590
None of you are walking away from this.

513
00:29:35,880 --> 00:29:37,070
No one is getting out alive.

514
00:29:44,030 --> 00:29:45,200
We go down together.

515
00:29:46,030 --> 00:29:47,270
Together!

516
00:30:05,750 --> 00:30:06,590
Ming,

517
00:30:10,550 --> 00:30:12,480
do you know how big a mess you've made?

518
00:30:14,110 --> 00:30:14,950
I do.

519
00:30:18,750 --> 00:30:20,160
If my mom weren't sick,

520
00:30:23,240 --> 00:30:24,830
I wouldn't be this desperate for money.

521
00:30:25,110 --> 00:30:26,240
You needed money.

522
00:30:27,270 --> 00:30:28,510
You should've told me.

523
00:30:29,480 --> 00:30:31,070
Instead, you went behind my back

524
00:30:31,960 --> 00:30:33,270
and did all this.

525
00:30:35,160 --> 00:30:36,550
What was I supposed to do?

526
00:30:47,350 --> 00:30:48,190
Ali,

527
00:30:52,110 --> 00:30:53,160
I told you before.

528
00:30:56,070 --> 00:30:57,400
Did you listen?

529
00:31:00,790 --> 00:31:03,030
If you hadn't dragged me
into working with Bai,

530
00:31:03,920 --> 00:31:06,070
would it have gone this far?

531
00:31:07,680 --> 00:31:08,640
I warned you

532
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:11,640
right after the first job.

533
00:31:11,640 --> 00:31:13,400
But you went crazy.

534
00:31:13,400 --> 00:31:14,920
And now you blame me?

535
00:31:21,750 --> 00:31:24,550
I'm an accomplice at worst.

536
00:31:27,440 --> 00:31:28,720
Let's not tear each other apart.

537
00:31:30,790 --> 00:31:31,720
What do you mean?

538
00:31:32,030 --> 00:31:33,000
You know what I mean.

539
00:31:35,070 --> 00:31:36,000
I'm turning myself in.

540
00:31:38,270 --> 00:31:41,550
Why should all your dirty deeds

541
00:31:41,550 --> 00:31:43,200
end up on my head?

542
00:31:44,550 --> 00:31:45,390
Calm down.

543
00:31:47,310 --> 00:31:48,510
It's not that bad yet.

544
00:31:49,060 --> 00:31:50,330
I can still figure something out.

545
00:31:50,830 --> 00:31:51,920
Figure out what?

546
00:31:51,920 --> 00:31:52,830
You keep

547
00:31:53,160 --> 00:31:54,070
figuring things out,

548
00:31:54,070 --> 00:31:55,880
I'll die without even knowing how.

549
00:31:56,680 --> 00:31:57,520
Easy.

550
00:31:57,590 --> 00:31:58,430
Easy.

551
00:31:59,350 --> 00:32:00,350
Think about your mom.

552
00:32:01,400 --> 00:32:02,440
If we all go down,

553
00:32:02,640 --> 00:32:03,680
who takes care of her?

554
00:32:03,680 --> 00:32:05,200
Don't talk about my mom.

555
00:32:07,270 --> 00:32:09,030
I'll take the fall.

556
00:32:09,030 --> 00:32:10,680
Then someone will look after her.

557
00:32:13,640 --> 00:32:14,750
You need money, right?

558
00:32:16,270 --> 00:32:17,110
I've got

559
00:32:18,480 --> 00:32:20,880
500,000 in cash at home.

560
00:32:22,110 --> 00:32:23,120
I'll give it all to you.

561
00:32:23,480 --> 00:32:24,510
Right now.

562
00:32:26,680 --> 00:32:27,520
Wait for me.

563
00:32:30,790 --> 00:32:31,630
Wang Li.

564
00:32:33,350 --> 00:32:34,920
Stop lying to me!

565
00:32:36,960 --> 00:32:38,160
At this point,

566
00:32:38,790 --> 00:32:41,400
we're tied together.

567
00:32:42,720 --> 00:32:43,560
I'm doing this

568
00:32:45,310 --> 00:32:46,440
for my daughter too.

569
00:32:52,030 --> 00:32:52,870
Wait for me.

570
00:32:58,200 --> 00:32:59,720
For your daughter, huh?

571
00:33:08,260 --> 00:33:10,780
(Wang Yimo)

572
00:33:18,640 --> 00:33:19,550
Sorry,

573
00:33:19,550 --> 00:33:22,200
the number you dialed
is currently unavailable.

574
00:33:22,210 --> 00:33:23,900
Darn it!

575
00:33:34,790 --> 00:33:35,630
Wang Yimo.

576
00:33:37,920 --> 00:33:39,030
You and your dad

577
00:33:39,590 --> 00:33:41,350
are same darn kind.

578
00:33:43,110 --> 00:33:44,830
Use me and dump me.

579
00:33:45,310 --> 00:33:47,200
Listen. I'm at the restaurant right now.

580
00:33:48,590 --> 00:33:50,960
You fix this now.

581
00:33:50,960 --> 00:33:52,400
Or I call the cops.

582
00:33:52,400 --> 00:33:54,310
Don't think I won't.

583
00:34:32,630 --> 00:34:33,630
Liars!

584
00:34:36,320 --> 00:34:37,160
Fine.

585
00:35:37,540 --> 00:35:43,030
♪Dreams of the past sleep in the chill♪

586
00:35:43,030 --> 00:35:46,480
♪Now I run toward the light♪

587
00:35:48,330 --> 00:35:53,590
♪What does the fire burn,
what does it reveal?♪

588
00:35:53,910 --> 00:35:57,560
♪Is the answer found when the sun rises♪

589
00:35:58,170 --> 00:36:02,460
♪If it's all a lie♪

590
00:36:03,650 --> 00:36:07,820
♪Should I tear it open?♪

591
00:36:09,150 --> 00:36:13,870
♪If it's all part of the journey♪

592
00:36:14,550 --> 00:36:19,400
♪Then face the blaze head-on♪

593
00:36:19,790 --> 00:36:24,260
♪Let the sun awaken my heart's crave♪

594
00:36:24,800 --> 00:36:30,530
♪Pain reminds me I'm alive♪

595
00:36:30,650 --> 00:36:35,460
♪The world can't take away every clear sky♪

596
00:36:36,110 --> 00:36:41,260
♪The hotter it gets, the fiercer I fight♪

597
00:36:41,570 --> 00:36:46,290
♪Let the sun burn away all I lean upon♪

598
00:36:46,630 --> 00:36:52,290
♪Leave me only what endures♪

599
00:36:52,400 --> 00:36:57,950
♪At the cliff's edge, all fear shatters♪

600
00:36:58,010 --> 00:37:04,960
♪With a grounded heart, a soul like fire♪
